                     <incipit xml:lang="gez" type="inscriptio">
                           <hi rend="rubric">ብስራተ፡ አብ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ትሩፍ፡ ረድ</hi>እ፡ ተናጋሪ<hi rend="rubric">፡</hi>
